urls.description: Indian untouchables - Dalits - and the lower caste people suffered a lot over millennia. But why was there no revolution by them? urls.title: Despite Millennia of Oppression, Why Did Not The Lower Caste And The Untouchables Revolt Against The Indian Upper Caste?
